{
  "texts": [
    "She does as she draws on past events and embeds them in a current situation.",
    "Paula's interplay of voice, gaze, and body enables Paula to give presence to absent others.",
    "Building on her prior actions, she molds her cognitive ecology (Hutchins 2010) in ways that allow her to make absent others present 'at hand.'",
    "After her envoicing of the others (\"oh well\"), Paula now moves from a general-you pronoun wording to using the first person (\"cause I would ask\").",
    "Her speech becomes fast-paced."
  ]
}